    "Therefore, the radar-centric waveform design is the basis of radar-centric ISAC systems.",
    "However, embedding the communication symbols inevitably introduces randomness into the radar waveform, resulting in the degradation of the detection capability.",
    "Therefore, effective receive signal processing techniques are critical to guaranteeing satisfactory sensing performance.",
    "In the following, we review the above two key techniques of radar-centric ISAC systems.",
    "• Beampattern modulation."
